    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Save Whales or Culture?</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>A C Bergmann letter on Oct 2 article warns whale hunting by Makah Indians would destroy whale sightseeing business</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>If the Makah whale hunt is allowed to proceed (news article, Oct. 2), the whale sightseeing business is finished -- whales won't come within a mile of any boat, and the owners might just as well put their boats up for sale now. Biologists may get a clue to the efficacy of communication between whales, but at a great price.</p>
        <p>A. C. BERGMANN  Minneapolis, Oct. 2, 1998</p>
      </block>
